Company spokesperson Lize Nel said: “As a company which proudly operates in the inner city, we decided to play our small part and helped clean the streets. “We understand the importance of living, working and playing in a city that is clean and safe.” Nel said they extended the invitation to other property companies to assist and clean the streets in front of their properties. “Collectively, as a business sector we can help the City of Tshwane. “We love the city and as a good corporate citizen we are always ready to help where possible.” - Staff Reporter